  {
    "hotel_id": "4915153",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/the-otto-hotel/hotel/hong-kong-hk.html",
    "name": "The OTTO Hotel",
    "detail": "The hotel is new, with minor teething problems but problems are fixed very quickly after I called them. It is a small hotel of about 56 rooms. Rooms are small as it is quite a standard in HK, but well equipped like most bigger hotels. It is very clean and security is good. The rooms are sound proof from traffic and street noises, but people talking from the next room can be heard faintly in our room. Very conveniently situated with TST MTR just 2-3 minutes across the street. A21 from the airport stops near Cameron Road junction and it is just 5 minutes walk across the street to the hotel. The hotel entrance is not very prominent so look out for McDonalds as landmark as it is just 2 shops away. There are many eating places, boutiques, shops and pharmacies nearby. We also found a General Practitioner doctor nearby when we needed treatment for gastro flu. I will definitely stay here again on my next trip to Hong Kong.",
